tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE holdings (
    holding_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_name VARCHAR(255),
    asset_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    quantity DECIMAL,
    price DECIMAL,
    total_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE portfolio_holdings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
    shares_owned INT,
    purchase_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    purchase_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_records (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
    transaction_type VARCHAR(10),
    transaction_date DATE,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    shares_traded INT
);

CREATE TABLE portfolio_holdings (
    holding_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ticker_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    quantity INT,
    purchase_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    purchase_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_records (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    holding_id INT,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(10),
    amount DECIMAL(10,2),
    transaction_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (holding_id) REFERENCES portfolio_holdings(holding_id)
);

CREATE TABLE trading_performance (
    trading_performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_id INT,
    neural_network_score FLOAT,
    trade_profit DECIMAL(10,2),
    trade_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (transaction_id) REFERENCES transaction_records(transaction_id)
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_records (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    holding_id INTEGER REFERENCES portfolio_holdings(holding_id),
    transaction_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    transaction_date DATE NOT NULL,
    transaction_amount DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE portfolio_holdings (
    holding_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    purchase_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    date_purchased DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_records (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    holding_id INT NOT NULL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    transaction_date DATE NOT NULL,
    transaction_amount DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trading_performance (
    performance_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    holding_id INT NOT NULL,
    net_profit DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    trade_date DATE NOT NULL,
    success BOOLEAN NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (
    network_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    network_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    training_data JSONB NOT NULL,
    training_iterations INT NOT NULL,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
